The [[BlasTech Industries/Legends|BlasTech]] '''E-11 Electroscope''' was a zooming scope for the [[E-11]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] [[Blaster rifle/Legends|rifle]]. An E-11 fitted with this electroscope somehow inflicted more damage per shot fired by increasing the precision and overenergizing the bolt, but in return had a much lower rate of fire. There were two zooming modes: automatic and manual zoom. The E-11 Electroscope could also be used on other rifles.

